11:30.520 --> 11:32.640
So, you can walk like that
everywhere you go.

11:33.200 --> 11:34.040
I'll do that.

11:34.440 --> 11:36.080
Yeah. Just sliding in.

11:36.160 --> 11:37.840
The other thing that has been congenial,

11:37.920 --> 11:39.800
has been constant, has been consistent,

11:39.880 --> 11:41.240
has been camouflage.

11:41.320 --> 11:43.400
-Right.
-And therefore, I'm giving you…

11:44.160 --> 11:45.720
-Oh, wow! Wow!
-Voila!

11:45.800 --> 11:47.200
-A camouflage jumper.
-Nice!

11:50.920 --> 11:52.000
-Get into the looks.
-Yes.

