26:14.320 --> 26:15.760
Ehh-- Newcomer.

26:16.120 --> 26:17.840
Newcomer. Newcomer. Newcomer.

26:17.920 --> 26:20.120
Keep saying that. Outsider-newcomer.
Outsider-newcomer.

