Okay. But if you have
any acting offers for me,

26:23.440 --> 26:26.400
please contact Sumukhi or Sapan
because no one else is!

26:27.120 --> 26:28.440
So, just make sure you do.

26:28.800 --> 26:30.720
And let me tell you, I'm not this mean.

26:30.920 --> 26:32.080
I'm really not this mean.

26:32.160 --> 26:33.400
I'm way worse!

26:34.160 --> 26:35.120
Remember that!

26:35.560 --> 26:36.680
Anyway…

26:37.920 --> 26:38.960
Alright, thanks, guys!

26:39.040 --> 26:43.120
And if everyone asks you how my
stand-up set-piece was,

26:43.560 --> 26:45.920
just like me, don't say "I'm speechless!"

26:46.000 --> 26:48.400
Just actually, have a
few good words to say.

26:48.480 --> 26:49.840
Alright, bye and toodles!

26:49.920 --> 26:50.840
Love you, guys! Thank you!

26:50.920 --> 26:52.760
Thank you for being
such a great audience!

26:56.560 --> 26:57.800
Mummy, how was it?

26:57.880 --> 26:59.960
It was so good! Guys, I was like this!

27:00.680 --> 27:02.400
So good, Karan. It was so good!

27:02.480 --> 27:03.840
He was amazing!

27:03.920 --> 27:04.960
You guys know he was amazing!

27:05.040 --> 27:06.560
-Please, clap once again.
