but in confined circles.

27:16.800 --> 27:18.400
And when it's not recorded…

27:19.120 --> 27:20.760
we say the darned-est things!

27:22.200 --> 27:24.000
I wish there was a camera
sometimes, you know,

27:24.080 --> 27:27.280
that would be material that was
made up of some other form of gold!

27:27.440 --> 27:30.840
But this is what we get when we
actually scratch the surface,

27:30.920 --> 27:31.800
not break it.

27:31.960 --> 27:34.360
So, we scratched the surface today,
but we had great fun doing it.

27:34.440 --> 27:36.800
So, thank you, guys!
Thank you, Amazon, <i>One Mic Stand</i> rocks.

27:37.120 --> 27:39.720
-Sapan and Sumukhi rock!
-Give it up for Karan Johar, everyone!

27:40.640 --> 27:42.120
Give it up for Sumukhi Suresh!

27:42.960 --> 27:44.040
I'm your host Sapan Verma,

27:44.120 --> 27:45.840
thank you so much!
It's <i>One Mic Stand!</i>

27:46.480 --> 27:47.600
-Bye! Good night!
-Thank you.

