When you started talking to the crowd
and they laughed

28:11.640 --> 28:13.840
when you did the natural thing of
addressing your mom…

28:13.920 --> 28:16.360
-Yeah.
-I think the most real Karan came out.

28:16.440 --> 28:17.840
Yeah, when you were like
"Mom, I'm so sorry."

28:17.920 --> 28:19.600
Everyone was like,
"Yeah, yeah. Mom. Right.

28:19.680 --> 28:20.960
Yeah, Karan. Same. Relate."

28:21.040 --> 28:23.120
I wouldn't have been able
to do this without you.

28:23.240 --> 28:24.680
I'm supposed to say that, I think.

28:24.840 --> 28:26.040
-No, no.
-Okay.

28:26.120 --> 28:27.560
-We get that a lot.
-But I genuinely wouldn't have

28:27.640 --> 28:29.000
been able to do this without you!

28:29.080 --> 28:31.520
Y'all had the right kind of energy and
it was amazing!

28:31.600 --> 28:33.880
You didn't stress me out and
nobody over-instructed me,

28:34.080 --> 28:35.080
and I think that's best.

28:35.160 --> 28:36.520
Thank you, guys!
This was great fun!

28:36.600 --> 28:38.400
-It was awesome!
-And I hope everyone enjoys it as well.
